                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Kingston Jamaica</placeName>\n                                        <date>26<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> Novr. 5611</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>My dear Sir,</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">A few days ago I received your letter of<lb/> the\n                                                  <date>26<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> August</date> last,\n                                        the detention of which has been owing to<lb/> some accident\n                                        having happened to the “<placeName>Kingston</placeName>”\n                                        which necessitated<lb/> her putting back. By the same\n                                        opportunity, I believe, the intermediate<lb/> Nos. of the\n                                        Occident have arrived, tho I have not yet received them.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I regret to inform you that the Cholera<lb/> has\n                                        been raging with unusual malignity in this\n                                                  <placeName>Island</placeName> for the<lb/> last\n                                        six weeks, to which fearful malady my lamented\n                                                  father<add>?</add><lb/>\n                                        <add>זצ\"ל</add> fell a victim on <date>Tuesday Evening last\n                                                  the 19<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi></date> Inst. As the<lb/>\n                                        <add>שבעה</add> is but just up, I have been unable to attend\n                                        to anything<lb/> hence my non-receipt of the Occidents just\n                                        arrived. I have handed<lb/> over the names of the\n                                        subscribers to this valuable periodical to <persName>Mr\n                                                  Lawton</persName><lb/> your agent, whose\n                                                  <add>?</add> will enable him to attend to the\n                                        pecuniary<lb/> part with success. Notwithstanding this, be\n                                        assured I will not<lb/> slacken in my endeavors to obtain\n                                        further subscribers thereto, as well<lb/> as to your\n                                                  partnered<add>?</add> publication of the “Jewish\n                                        Advocate.” Still, it is<lb/> my duty to tell you candidly, I\n                                        do not apprehend any degree of success,<lb/> as the distress\n                                        of our Community is beyond expression. For some time<lb/>\n                                        (indeed since the appearance of the Cholera amongst us)\n                                        Business has<lb/> been at a complete stand, and the means of\n                                        the <hi rend=\"underline\">few</hi> who are blessed</p>\n                              "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3v698z41/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
